origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2bbe641a315f23f4d24cff75982da020_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2bbe641a315f23f4d24cff75982da020_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-566d22c60f5b981a931c364a6b9dbeb4_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"949\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-566d22c60f5b981a931c364a6b9dbeb4\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-566d22c60f5b981a931c364a6b9dbeb4_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;949&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"949\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-566d22c60f5b981a931c364a6b9dbeb4\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-566d22c60f5b981a931c364a6b9dbeb4_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-566d22c60f5b981a931c364a6b9dbeb4_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d822dde59fbeba74d712f2e3b42c807_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"489\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-8d822dde59fbeba74d712f2e3b42c807\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8d822dde59fbeba74d712f2e3b42c807_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;489&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"489\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-8d822dde59fbeba74d712f2e3b42c807\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8d822dde59fbeba74d712f2e3b42c807_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d822dde59fbeba74d712f2e3b42c807_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"NR3xwuHv\">只是，在夜深人静的时候，也会难免伤心呢……</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-59b007c280847ab83f7ddac0150a44c0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1146\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-59b007c280847ab83f7ddac0150a44c0\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-59b007c280847ab83f7ddac0150a44c0_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;1146&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1146\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-59b007c280847ab83f7ddac0150a44c0\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-59b007c280847ab83f7ddac0150a44c0_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-59b007c280847ab83f7ddac0150a44c0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Q7_W2llV\">第二天，我们的郑同学被前来送快递的大叔吵醒，但从大叔的闪烁的目光中，他（她？）感觉到了一丝不对劲，随后他（她？）看到镜子中自己的脸……</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-455c5d967cbbd97ec02838f74d1686fa_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1049\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-455c5d967cbbd97ec02838f74d1686fa\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-455c5d967cbbd97ec02838f74d1686fa_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;1049&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1049\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-455c5d967cbbd97ec02838f74d1686fa\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-455c5d967cbbd97ec02838f74d1686fa_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-455c5d967cbbd97ec02838f74d1686fa_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"sdDEViP5\">而他（她？）的反应居然是……</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f4910f4f04412aecd304b8d7a84678be_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1363\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-f4910f4f04412aecd304b8d7a84678be\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f4910f4f04412aecd304b8d7a84678be_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;1363&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1363\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-f4910f4f04412aecd304b8d7a84678be\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f4910f4f04412aecd304b8d7a84678be_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f4910f4f04412aecd304b8d7a84678be_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"p7_U5sDy\">（这小孩……）</p><p data-pid=\"p8lbJ4RT\">当然他（她？）还是搞清了状况……</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-88100f109927b13642f7b89abd5fd719_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"915\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-88100f109927b13642f7b89abd5fd719\" class=\"origi